description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Bodyweight Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Groove Session vibe.
The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity. The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Stabilize and strengthen your whole body with Peter and Sera Moon from a sunny poolside location in Miami....
